ClientVersion: string; The Zero Trust client version at the time of upload.
DeviceID: string; The device ID that performed the posture upload.
DeviceManufacturer: string; The manufacturer of the device that the Zero Trust client is running on.
DeviceModel: string; The model of the device that the Zero Trust client is running on.
DeviceName: string; The name of the device that the Zero Trust client is running on.
DeviceSerialNumber: string; The serial number of the device that the Zero Trust client is running on.
DeviceType: string; The Zero Trust client operating system type.
Email: string; The email used to register the device with the Zero Trust client.
OSVersion: string; The operating system version at the time of upload.
PolicyID: string; The posture check ID associated with this device posture result.
PostureCheckName: string; The name of the posture check associated with this device posture result.
PostureCheckType: string; The type of the Zero Trust client check or service provider check.
PostureEvaluatedResult: bool; Whether this posture upload passes the associated posture check, given the requirements posture check at the time of the timestamp.
PostureExpectedJSON: object; JSON object of what the posture check expects from the Zero Trust client.
PostureReceivedJSON: object; JSON object of what the Zero Trust client actually uploads.
Timestamp: int or string; The date and time the corresponding device posture upload was performed (for example, '2021-07-27T00:01:07Z').
UserUID: string; The uid of the user who registered the device.
